lead_paragraph: Tall Jamaican diver Yona Knight-Wisdom hopes he has inspired others to break down barriers and banish stereotypes after becoming the first male diver from the Caribbean island to qualify for the Olympics.

headline.print_headline: Jamaican Diver Hoping to Make Splash for Diversity
